018package org.tquadrat.foundation.util.internal;
019
020import static org.apiguardian.api.API.Status.INTERNAL;
021
022import java.util.Comparator;
023import java.util.NoSuchElementException;
024import java.util.SortedMap;
025import java.util.function.Supplier;
026
027import org.apiguardian.api.API;
028import org.tquadrat.foundation.annotation.ClassVersion;
029import org.tquadrat.foundation.lang.Lazy;
030import org.tquadrat.foundation.util.LazyMap;
031import org.tquadrat.foundation.util.LazySortedMap;
032
033/**
034 *  The implementation for
035 *  {@link LazyMap}.
036 *
037 *  @extauthor Thomas Thrien - thomas.thrien@tquadrat.org
038 *  @version $Id: LazySortedMapImpl.java 966 2022-01-04 22:28:49Z tquadrat $
039 *  @since 0.0.5
040 *
041 *  @param <K> The type of keys maintained by this map
042 *  @param <V> The type of mapped values
043 *
044 *  @UMLGraph.link
045 */
046@ClassVersion( sourceVersion = "$Id: LazySortedMapImpl.java 966 2022-01-04 22:28:49Z tquadrat $" )
047@API( status = INTERNAL, since = "0.0.5" )
048public final class LazySortedMapImpl<K,V> extends LazyMapImpl<K,V> implements LazySortedMap<K,V>
049{
050        /*--------------*\
051    ====** Constructors **=====================================================
052        \*--------------*/
053    /**
054     *  Creates a new {@code LazySortedMapImpl<K,V>} instance.
055     *
056     *  @param  doPopulate  {@code true} if the provided supplier will put
057     *      values to the map on initialisation, {@code false} if it will
058     *      create an empty map.
059     *  @param  supplier    The supplier that initialises the internal map for
060     *      this instance on the first it is needed.
061     */
062    public LazySortedMapImpl( final boolean doPopulate, final Supplier<? extends SortedMap<K, V>> supplier )
063    {
064        super( doPopulate, supplier );
065    }   //  LazySortedMapImpl<K,V>()
066
067    /**
068     *  Creates a new {@code LazyMapImpl} instance that is initialised with the
069     *  given value.
070     *
071     *  @param  value   The initialisation value.
072     */
073    @SuppressWarnings( "TypeMayBeWeakened" )
074    public LazySortedMapImpl( final SortedMap<K,V> value )
075    {
076        super( value );
077    }   //  LazySortedMapImpl()
078
079        /*---------*\
080    ====** Methods **==========================================================
081        \*---------*/
082    /**
083     *  {@inheritDoc}<br>
084     *  <br>A call to this method initialises the lazy map.
085     */
086    @Override
087    public final Comparator<? super K> comparator() { return holder().get().comparator(); }
088
089    /**
090     *  {@inheritDoc}
091     */
092    @Override
093    public final K firstKey()
094    {
095        if( isEmpty() )
096        {
097            //noinspection NewExceptionWithoutArguments
098            throw new NoSuchElementException();
099        }
100
101        final var retValue = holder().get().firstKey();
102
103        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
104        return retValue;
105    }   //  firstKey()
106
107    /**
108     *  {@inheritDoc}<br>
109     *  <br>A call to this method initialises the lazy map.
110     */
111    @Override
112    public final SortedMap<K,V> headMap( final K toKey )
113    {
114        final var retValue = holder().get().headMap( toKey );
115
116        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
117        return retValue;
118    }   //  headMap
119
120    /**
121     *  {@inheritDoc}
122     */
123    @SuppressWarnings( "unchecked" )
124    @Override
125    protected final Lazy<? extends SortedMap<K,V>> holder() { return (Lazy<SortedMap<K,V>>) super.holder(); }
126
127    /**
128     *  {@inheritDoc}
129     */
130    @Override
131    public final K lastKey()
132    {
133        if( isEmpty() )
134        {
135            //noinspection NewExceptionWithoutArguments
136            throw new NoSuchElementException();
137        }
138
139        final var retValue = holder().get().lastKey();
140
141        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
142        return retValue;
143    }   //  lastKey()
144
145    /**
146     *  {@inheritDoc}<br>
147     *  <br>A call to this method initialises the lazy map.
148     */
149    @Override
150    public final SortedMap<K,V> subMap( final K fromKey, final K toKey )
151    {
152        final var retValue = holder().get().subMap( fromKey, toKey );
153
154        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
155        return retValue;
156    }   //  subMap
157
158    /**
159     *  {@inheritDoc}<br>
160     *  <br>A call to this method initialises the lazy map.
161     */
162    @Override
163    public final SortedMap<K,V> tailMap( final K fromKey )
164    {
165        final var retValue = holder().get().tailMap( fromKey );
166
167        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
168        return retValue;
169    }   //  tailMap
170}
171//  class LazySortedMapImpl
